{
  "stem": "11205.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and we run away, and I was wearing a-- like a raincoat over my winter coat, and it was a light beige color.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And-- and I know it fell a bomb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was covered with the air [? of ?] the bomb.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, spill it out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then the airplanes were so low that I felt that my white coat, they could see.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, and this last quite a while.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then it got dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we start to crawl on-- on this field.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we couldn't find the highway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I was stuck with a friend of mine and from far, I could-- when we were running, I could see my brother and my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, they were separate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I could see them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we couldn't find anybody, and it was start to rain.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and this-- my friend, he was sitting on a rucksack, and we had a blanket, all covered with the blanket, wet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- and overhead on the rock, we saw already a fight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Fighting, you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could see red, the burning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when-- then he started, you know, now we will be caught with the Germans, and anyway.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As I was sitting, I felt the ground was shaking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I thought, you know what, [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He said, it could be already the Germans coming, and we followed this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, it doesn't matter what-- whoever it is, we can't stay on the field.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we found it was a hospital, a-- a Russian hospital evacuated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they've been on-- on trucks, a lot of wounded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was such a big, you know, a long-- and it was mud.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they couldn't, they had to stop.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
